creator: JMDSOFT Company
descriptionHtml:
Collect 3 or more fresh fruits to overcome challenges and enjoy hundreds of different and fun stages.
Compete with your friends and see who can get the highest score

[How to play]
▷ Achieve your goals at all levels and get the best score
▷ Match 3 or 4 or more fruits of the same color
▷ If you match 5 fruits of the same color in a row, you can make a multi-colored candy with a tremendous effect.
▷ Match 4 fruits of the same color into a square to create a cute foot jelly
▷ Collect coins to buy powerful items.
▷ Challenge your friends every stage.

[Game Features]
▷ 3 Match Puzzle Game
▷ Maximum fun and strong addictive game.
▷ Hundreds of challenging and unique stages!
▷ Offline Mode: No Wi-Fi or Internet connection is required in the game. Everyone, young and old, enjoy together
▷ New level design: Fruits don't always flow from top to bottom. It can flow from bottom to top, right to left, and left to right. Check your direction and succeed in the challenge
▷ Fruits Joy Booster to help you: A powerful item that helps you solve goals, break all blocks and help you solve puzzles
▷ Supports all resolutions: Whether vertical or horizontal, large or small screens, everything is at your disposal ~~!
▷ Ranking system: There are various rankings such as star ranking, highest level ranking, and score ranking. Play with your friends
▷ Endless Stage: Levels 20 ~ 50 are always updated every two weeks.

Compete with your friends and see who can get the highest score

[How to play]
▷ Achieve your goals at all levels and get the best score
▷ Match 3 or 4 or more fruits of the same color
▷ If you match 5 fruits of the same color in a row, you can make a multi-colored candy with a tremendous effect.
▷ Match 4 fruits of the same color into a square to create a cute foot jelly
▷ Collect coins to buy powerful items.
▷ Challenge your friends every stage.

[Game Features]
▷ 3 Match Puzzle Game
▷ Maximum fun and strong addictive game.
▷ Hundreds of challenging and unique stages!
▷ Offline Mode: No Wi-Fi or Internet connection is required in the game. Everyone, young and old, enjoy together
▷ New level design: Fruits don't always flow from top to bottom. It can flow from bottom to top, right to left, and left to right. Check your direction and succeed in the challenge
▷ Fruits Joy Booster to help you: A powerful item that helps you solve goals, break all blocks and help you solve puzzles
▷ Supports all resolutions: Whether vertical or horizontal, large or small screens, everything is at your disposal ~~!
▷ Ranking system: There are various rankings such as star ranking, highest level ranking, and score ranking. Play with your friends
▷ Endless Stage: Levels 20 ~ 50 are always updated every two weeks.
